<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alpha Solução Clean - Checklist</title>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="default">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Checklist Alpha">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='80' font-size='80'>📋</text></svg>">
    <style>
        :root {
            --blue-dark: #1e40af;
            --blue: #2563eb;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --text-secondary: #64748b;
            --shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: #f8fafc;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .header {
            background: var(--card);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .logo-alpha { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--blue-dark); }
        .logo-solucao { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--blue); }
        .logo-tagline { font-size: 7px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase; }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            background: var(--card);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .nav-link {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            white-space: nowrap;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            background: var(--card);
        }
        .nav-link.voltar { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--blue); }
        .nav-link.planilha { background: #16a34a; color: #fff; border-color: #16a34a; }

        iframe {
            width: 100%;
            flex: 1;
            border: none;
            min-height: 85vh;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            background: var(--card);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo-alpha">ALPHA</div>
        <div class="logo-solucao">SOLUÇÃO CLEAN</div>
        <div class="logo-tagline">Checklist de Serviço</div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="admin.html" class="nav-link voltar">⬅ Painel</a>
        <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1a2CXDRC9N6IdAVKUgX3mMRHPwkSf2cUJC6yf5QSMEjo/edit?usp=drivesdk" target="_blank" class="nav-link planilha">📊 Planilha</a>
        <a href="https://calendar.google.com" target="_blank" class="nav-link">📅 Agenda</a>
    </div>

    <iframe src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdy8ZMtkVCzz-db3rKSkYcN7uu_9wfx_ujvOZm4nETg9jv0Tw/viewform?embedded=true"></iframe>

    <div class="footer">
        💡 Adicione à tela inicial: ⋮ > Adicionar à tela | Alpha Solução Clean
    </div>
</body>
</html>
